Garden suppliers run the Garden Centre, stores that sells various bagged plants and trees for player-owned houses. They can be found wandering around Falador Park and the Farming Guild.

Their stock level is specific to each single world, so once they run out of stock you can buy more bagged plants by hopping worlds.
